How configure JAVA 9 in our machine and create a program in this version

    STEPS:
        1: We need to install JDK 9, you can to visit the next page: https://adoptopenjdk.net/releases.html?variant=openjdk9&jvmVariant=hotspot
           and select OpenJDK 9.

        2: We can open IntelliJ IDEA and create a new project.

        3: Then we must select File -> Project Structure -> Artifacts -> Button Plus -> Add JAR -> From modules with dependencies
           -> Select class with main method -> Apply -> OK.

        4: Select Build